PortSystem                  1.0
PortGroup                   github 1.0

github.setup                atlas-engineer cl-webengine 0fd81be936b547e008c8f7809b2df962a79da490
version                     20210225
revision                    0

checksums                   rmd160  819aeebe25e83ccb8cb1af0e060bd171098c41fc \
